```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(readr)
library(janitor)

vend_data<-read.csv("vend-created_date-for-outlet.csv") %>%
  clean_names()
vend_data %>%
  group_by(supplier_code)%>%
  ggplot(aes(x=supplier_code,y=sell_through_rate)) +geom_col()+coord_flip()
```
